Banco Cruzeiro do Sul (BM&F Bovespa:CZR4) is a Brazil-based bank mainly engaged in the consumer financing segment. It offers redit, investment, brokerage and consulting services, as well as a range of financial products. It also offers public bond market intermediation and loans.
The bank's products are distributed in Brazil through a network of banking correspondents which included more than 360 small and midsized companies.
Currently the bank is headquartered in SÃ£o Paulo and is owned by Indio da Costa family.
